Mix mayonnaise and curry sauce in small bowl. Spread 3 tablespoons mayonnaise mixture in 2-inch wide strip down center of tortilla. Top with 1/2 cup chicken and 1/3 cup coleslaw blend. Repeat, using remaining ingredients. Fold one end of tortilla up about 2 inches over filling, fold right and left sides over folded end, overlapping; repeat. Serve at once.